OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779718268
OL,3,CPhillipson's push for watchdog to
OL,4,Creview childcare market criticised as
OL,5,C'odd'
OL,7,FBridget Phillipson's call for the
OL,8,Fcompetition watchdog to look into
OL,9,Fhidden extra charges in Government-
OL,10,Ffunded childcare is "odd" at a time
OL,11,Fwhen the sector is "grossly
OL,12,Funderfunded", the head of the Early
OL,13,FYears Alliance has said.
OL,15,FEligible working parents in England
OL,16,Fare able to get 30 hours a week of
OL,17,Ffree childcare for children aged
OL,18,Fbetween nine months and four years old.
OL,26,@rD@UOUrD@YO]sD@TOUtD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
