OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779718268
OL,3,CPhillipson's push for watchdog to
OL,4,Creview childcare market criticised as
OL,5,C'odd'
OL,7,FBut ministers are concerned about the
OL,8,Fadditional costs parents face to
OL,9,Fsecure places.
OL,11,FThe Education Secretary will ask the
OL,12,FCompetition and Markets Authority
OL,13,F(CMA) to look into extra charges
OL,14,Fparents have encountered ` including
OL,15,Fin waiting list deposits, compulsory
OL,16,Fadd-ons or additional hours to access
OL,17,Fwhat they are entitled to.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779718268
OL,3,CPhillipson's push for watchdog to
OL,4,Creview childcare market criticised as
OL,5,C'odd'
OL,7,FSome parents are also expected to pay
OL,8,Ffor meals or drinks, snacks, nappies
OL,9,Fand sun cream as well as one-off
OL,10,Factivities such as special outings.
OL,12,FMs Phillipson will tell the regulator
OL,13,Fto begin an investigation into
OL,14,Fchildcare providers as early as
OL,15,FTuesday, the Financial Times first
OL,16,Freported.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779718268
OL,3,CPhillipson's push for watchdog to
OL,4,Creview childcare market criticised as
OL,5,C'odd'
OL,7,FThe CMA will also be asked to examine
OL,8,Fwhether private equity companies
OL,9,Foperating in the childcare sector are
OL,10,Fdriving up costs, according to the
OL,11,Fnewspaper.
OL,13,FNeil Leitch, chief executive of Early
OL,14,FYears Alliance, said the watchdog
OL,15,Fshould instead investigate the
OL,16,Funderfunding of the industry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779718268
OL,3,CPhillipson's push for watchdog to
OL,4,Creview childcare market criticised as
OL,5,C'odd'
OL,7,FHe told BBC Radio 4's Today programme
OL,8,Fon Monday: "Regardless of the family's
OL,9,Fincome, socioeconomic status of the
OL,10,Fchild, every child should have the
OL,11,Fright to care and education.
OL,13,F"But to make that happen, you have to
OL,14,Fadequately fund the sector.
OL,16,F"And what I find sort of odd at the
OL,17,Fmoment is the Government knows that's
OL,18,Fnot the case.
OL,20,F"And I have to ask, why now ask the
OL,21,FCMA to look at this?
OL,26,@pD@LOUuD@AOUxD@AOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779718268
OL,3,CPhillipson's push for watchdog to
OL,4,Creview childcare market criticised as
OL,5,C'odd'
OL,7,F"If you're going to ask the CMA to
OL,8,Flook at anything, why don't you ask
OL,9,Fthem to look at whether the sector is
OL,10,Fadequately funded, because just about
OL,11,Fevery single financial institution
OL,12,Fthat's looked into the costs of early
OL,13,Fyears care and education has said that
OL,14,Fthis sector is grossly underfunded."
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@dO]
