OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779718268
OL,3,CPhillipson's push for watchdog to
OL,4,Creview childcare market criticised as
OL,5,C'odd'
OL,7,FMr Leitch continued: "I can't help
OL,8,Ffeeling this is a bit of a PR exercise
OL,9,Fto demonstrate that the Government's
OL,10,Fon the side of parents.
OL,12,F"If it really wants to be on the side
OL,13,Fof parents, fund the sector
OL,14,Fadequately."
OL,16,FMs Phillipson's move will come as Sir
OL,17,FKeir Starmer's Government seeks to
OL,18,Fease the impact on the cost of living
OL,19,Ffrom the Iran war.
OL,26,@oD@VOUtD@AOUvD@LO]
